1. How to run jupyter notebook using pyspark?
Please set below parameters in your .bashrc file

export PYSPARK_DRIVER_PYTHON=/usr/anaconda2/bin/jupyter
export PYSPARK_DRIVER_PYTHON_OPTS='notebook'
export PYSPARK_PYTHON=/usr/anaconda2/bin/python
#export SPARK_MAJOR_VERSION=2
export PYSPARK_SUBMIT_ARGS="--packages com.databricks:spark-csv_2.10:1.0.3 --master yarn-client"
